General.Name: Cantor Equity Partners, Inc. Class A Ordinary Shares
General.Description: Cantor Equity Partners, Inc. does not have significant operations. It intends to effect a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses in the financial services, healthcare, real estate services, technology, and software industries. The company was formerly known as CF Acquisition Corp. A. and changed its name to Cantor Equity Partners, Inc. in June 2024. Cantor Equity Partners, Inc. was incorporated in 2020 and is based in New York, New York.
